Parameters.Description: The ID of the Account that the document belongs to

Parameters.Description: For `individualGovernmentId` `fieldId`, you could specify the `documentType`. Possible values are `GOVT_ID`, `DRIVING_LICENSE`, `PASSPORT_CARD` and `PASSPORT`

Fields.Name: desc
Fields.Description: A description of the credentials

Fields.Name: type

Fields.Description: A list of IP addresses that are allowed to use the key (left empty for no restrictions)

Fields.Name: source
Fields.Description: An SRN representing an account that the funds will be retrieved from

Fields.Name: sourceCurrency
Fields.Description: The currency (ISO 3166-1 Alpha-3) to withdraw from the source wallet

Fields.Name: sourceAmount
Fields.Description: The amount to withdraw from the source, in units of `sourceCurrency` (only include `sourceAmount` OR `destAmount`, not both)

Fields.Name: dest
Fields.Description: An account, wallet, digital currency address or bank account to send the digital currency to. (for bitcoin address use `bitcoin:[address]`)

Fields.Name: destCurrency
Fields.Description: The currency (ISO 3166-1 Alpha-3) to deposit. if not provided, the deposit will be the same as the withdrawal currency (no exchange performed)

Fields.Name: destAmount
Fields.Description: Specifies the total amount of `destCurrency` to deposit (only include `sourceAmount` OR `destAmount`, not both)

Fields.Name: message
Fields.Description: An optional user visible message to be sent with the transaction

Fields.Name: notifyUrl
Fields.Description: An optional URL that Wyre will `POST` a status callback to

Fields.Name: autoConfirm
Fields.Description: An optional parameter to automatically confirm the transfer order

Fields.Name: customId
Fields.Description: An optional custom identifier to tag the transfer

Fields.Name: amountIncludesFees
Fields.Description: This optional flag, when true indicates that the amount provided (`sourceAmount` OR `destAmount`) will be treated as already including the fees

Fields.Name: preview
Fields.Description: This optional flag, when true, creates a quote transfer object, but does not execute a real transfer

Fields.Name: muteMessages
Fields.Description: This optional flag, when true, will disable all outbound emails and messages to the destination

Fields.Name: profileFields
Fields.Description: An array containing objects with `fieldId` and `value` properties specifying which fields to update to the given values

Fields.Name: secretKey
Fields.Description: The client-generated secret key

Fields.Name: subscribeTo
Fields.Description: The SRN for the object being subscribed to (whenever this object is updated, the callback will be triggered)

Fields.Name: type
Fields.Description: The type of account, currently `INDIVIDUAL` is the only supported value

Fields.Name: country
Fields.Description: The country of the account holder. For individuals this is the country of residence. (Currently we only support US accounts)

Fields.Name: subaccount
Fields.Description: When true, the newly created account will be a custodial subaccount owner by the caller. Otherwise, the account will be a standalone non-custodial account.

Fields.Name: profileFields
Fields.Description: An array of the Fields submitted at the time of Account creation. You can submit as many or as few fields as you need at the time of Account creation.

Fields.Name: referrerAccountId
Fields.Description: Supply your own Account ID when creating noncustodial accounts. This field is used to track which account referred the new account into our system

Fields.Name: disableEmail
Fields.Description: Prevent all outbound emails to the account

Fields.Name: blockchain
Fields.Description: The blockchain to attach (can be `BTC`, `ETH`, `ALL`, or multiple currencies with commas e.g. `BTC,ETH`)

Fields.Name: notifyUrl
Fields.Description: The webhook URL that will be notified of any changes in status for transfers involving this blockchain attachment

Fields.Name: muteMessages
Fields.Description: When `true` indicates that the resulting transfers should not dispatch email notifications

Fields.Name: name
Fields.Description: A unique identifier for the wallet (could be a client-generated user identifier)

Fields.Name: callbackUrl
Fields.Description: A callback URL to receive updates related to this wallet

Fields.Name: type
Fields.Description: The type of wallet you are creating (`DEFAULT` or `ENTERPRISE`)

Fields.Name: notes
Fields.Description: Notes about the wallet

Fields.Description: Full Street Address

Fields.Name: state
Fields.Description: State Code

Fields.Name: postalCode
Fields.Description: Only numbers

Fields.Name: country
Fields.Description: Alpha-2 Country Code
